Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time I was here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I woke them and ended up\Nwith a mane full of bats!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for being\Nmy basket holder, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Basket holder? I thought\NI was your bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh yes, yes.\NThat of course, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh for once I wish\Nunicorn magic wasn't so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,luminescent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, you'll wake the\Nbats! Turn that off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! Oooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing impaired subtitles\Nby YayPonies\NWe have muffins!\Nhttps://yp1.yayponies.no/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.40,0:01:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so glad{\i0}\N{\i1} you two could come.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. We so\Nrarely get a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to relax and just visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's usually some crisis\Nwe have to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.74,0:01:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony always needs\Nour help. But today--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,HELP! Twilight! There's\Nsomething wrong with Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.34,0:01:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!\NAll of the sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,my scales just started\Nglowing and burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Little is known\Nabout dragon culture,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is a phenomenon\Nwe've seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the Call of\NThe Dragon Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons glow whenever\Nthe Dragon Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,has need of them\Nin the Dragonlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! How\Ndo I make it stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way to end the\Nsummons is to answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You must journey\Nto the Dragonlands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and see what is\Nexpected of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Dragonlands\Nare full of... dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're\Nghastly creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-oh not you of\Ncourse, Spikey Wikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But remember that\Nrotten Garble?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How could\NI forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He would have burnt us to a\Ncrisp if you weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have to go to\Nthe Dragonlands,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,would you two come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Oh my goodness! I'd\Nlove to! We are sadly lacking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,any information on dragon\Nculture and customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I could research them, maybe\Neven write an article!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be my chance to\Nmake a great contribution
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to the knowledge of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And be there for\NSpike, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragonlands are\Nparticularly dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for ponies. It would\Nbe wise to be discreet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sure I still have\Nthe dragon costume we used
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the last time we snuck into\Nthe Dragonlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we might\Nwant something
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a little more\Npractical this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it may\Nbe practical,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but this disguise isn't\Nflattering in the slightest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not supposed\Nto be flattering;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's supposed to blend in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,SHHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look. It's our old\Nfriend, Sparkle Warkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure your pony friends\Ndidn't give you a pony name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to see\Nyou too, Garble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say it was nice\Nto see you. It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I not clear about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's my rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really? Then why\Naren't you sitting on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons of Equestria! Hear me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been Dragon\NLord for longer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,than many of you\Ncan remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And my reign has\Nbeen extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,AGREE WITH ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Torch! Torch! Torch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dragon Lord Torch, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's his daughter,\NPrincess Ember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't even look\Nat her if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you want\NTorch to eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fascinating! Dragons\Nare notoriously reckless,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but they do whatever\Nthe Dragon Lord says.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately,\Naccording to dragon law,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it is time for me to\Nstep down. Sad, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,BE SAD!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I have\Nsummoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To compete for the throne\Nin the Gauntlet of Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whomever has the\Nstrength and fortitude
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to retrieve this\NBloodstone Scepter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,from the heart of\Nthe Flamecano
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,will be crowned Lord\Nof the Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When the scepter disappeared,\Nthe dragons stopped glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We are learning so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah ah ah ....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,choo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. You even\Nsneeze like a pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gauntlet is dangerous,\Nfor I designed it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Only dragons with my ferocity,\Nstrength and determination
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,will be able to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We will gather at the cliff\Nwhen the sun is at its peak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be Dragon\NLord or dragon toast
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and I stopped glowing so\Nlet's sneak out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're\Ngoing, little dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, hi Your Lordship.\NI was just going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get to leave\Nunless I say you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, look at him!\NHe's just a runt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, he doesn't even\Nwant to compete. Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He is rather tiny. I could\Nsquish him with my pinky claw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a joke;\Nit was a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When I want you to laugh\NI will say "BE AMUSED"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Your Lordship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I don't understand\Ndragon customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Another reason why\NI shouldn't compete.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, little\Ndragon. I release you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,To prepare for the gauntlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not. You're not\Nmuch bigger than that runt
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just sent home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm smarter than most\Nof these boulderheads
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Being smart won't help\Nyou win this gauntlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was designed for a\Nbig strong dragon to win
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because it takes a big\Nstrong dragon to lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I SAID NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate when he does that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When I become Dragon Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make burps an\Nofficial greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, you? Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When I win, I will\Npillage Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,for all their pillows!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should these\Nponies be comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,while we sleep on rocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nothing.\NWhen I'm in charge,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the first thing I'll do is get\Nrevenge on those puny ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll regret they\Never crossed Garble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take whatever\Nwe want from Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and burn the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh. I can't\Nbelieve I'm saying this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but I hope that\Nburping dragon wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,None of them can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria is in big trouble\Nif any of them are in charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But what\Ncan we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing to\Ndo and only I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to win the\NGauntlet of Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you\Nhave to win the Gauntlet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only way to protect\NEquestria from the dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard them. They have\Nhorrible plans for ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,if they win! So somehow,\NI have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be another way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, if you win,\Nyou'd have to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. But there's no other\Nway to keep my friends safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're\Nstaying to compete,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,then we're staying\Nto cheer you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I released\Nyou, Tiny One.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to compete. I\Nam a dragon, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? You\Ncan't even fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All dragons are\Nwelcome to compete,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,for they do so at\Ntheir own peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying to Flamecano Island is\Nthe first of many challenges
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you will face in your quest to\Nfind the Bloodstone Scepter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck. Just kidding,\NI hope you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Garble, I was\Nplanning on swimming anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,SPIKE!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Ember!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Only saving your\Nungrateful scales!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that seaweed just talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies? What are\Nthey doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They're my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends? Dragons\Ndon't do friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this dragon does!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. I don't care as long\Nas none of you get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a gauntlet to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought your dad said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what my dad said!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show him and\Neverydragon who thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a little "Princess"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,there are better things\Nthan being big and strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me here, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha! I knew you'd do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pony friends made you soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,For what? I didn't\Nsay thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you even smell like ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it coming from over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I uh, robbed some ponies\Non my way over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I like your style.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I met you before?\NYou kinda look like--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My uh, old neighbor,\Nuh, Sandy Rockbeach!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid slingtails\Nknocked me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've wasted enough time\Nmaking small talk. Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're too small\Nto win this. I'm funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you cover for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have had\None less competitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I could ask you the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have told\NGarble about my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes. That looks rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's what\Nmakes it a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? Those\Nboulders are huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what if we\Nwork together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You fly me up there and\NI'll help you look out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,for boulders like a\Nsecond set of eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,PSSST!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's a good\Nidea to team up with Ember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know her too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I do know she could have\Ntold Garble about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but she didn't. I\Nthink we can trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Her behavior does seem\Ncontradictory to everything
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've noted about\Ndragons so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You. Little fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've thought about it and your\Nplan makes sense. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Great! It's a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, this doesn't\Nmean we're gonna pick flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,or exchange necklaces or\Nwhatever pony friends do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck. We'll\Nmeet you at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull up, there's\None on your tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go left!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we go through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Oh,\Nthat looks scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Spike, I wouldn't have\Nmade it this far without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:14:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess, if you want to, we\Ncould keep working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, just until we\Nget through that tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you made it!\NOh, we were so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,About us? Pssh. That\Ntunnel was cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, how did you\Ntwo get through?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh thanks, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.09,0:15:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing? You just risked\Neverything to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're putting themselves\Nin danger just to support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what friends do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have anyone\Nwho looks out for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. Unless\NI count you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...which I don't because we\Nwere only helping each other
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,get through the tunnel and now\Nwe're through the tunnel so,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's only one\Nwinner, one scepter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and one Dragon Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess it's every\Ndragon for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. So we aren't\Nreally friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if we were in ponyland
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:16:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but like I said, dragons\Ndon't do friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\NEmber ditched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh you're better off. She was\Nonly looking out for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just like all\Nthe other dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not, though. I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She saved me, even when\Nshe didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what she says.\NThat makes us friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just me or\Nhave we seen this crevice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,three times already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of hard to tell.\NThey all look the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for this one! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm the only\Ndragon to make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're not!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not losing to a puny\Npony-loving dragon like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to\Ndo something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ember! I thought it was\Nevery dragon for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what friends do.\NAnd I am. I mean we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I never should have\Nleft you back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, please don't make me\Ntalk about my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What the--?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! Get the scepter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaaagh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick and tired of you\Ntwo helping each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons don't do helping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,These dragons do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You? You have the scepter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means that you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Lord.\NDragon Lord Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw. Dragon Lord Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Uh,now go start\Nyour long journey home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And give every dragon\Nyou see on the way a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell them why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, but that'll be\Nsuper embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I command you to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dragon Lord Spike". Hmm.\NHas a nice ring to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Lord Ember\Nsounds a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No. You're\Nthe Dragon Lord now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Lord is whoever\Nbrings the scepter back
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you'll\Nmake a great leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just doing this\Nto protect the ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but I know you'll protect them\Njust as well as I would have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely. My home is in\NEquestria with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll have at least\None friend here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I don't know if\NI like it, but OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ember? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you didn't think\NI could do it, but I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I expressly told you NOT TO\NDO IT! Because you're not--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'm not big and strong!\NI know! But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I won anyway. So, maybe it\Ntakes more than just being
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,big and strong to be\Na good Dragon Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.64,0:20:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong, Ember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not be big, but\Nyou are strong. And smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And perhaps that counts\Nfor more than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will make\Nan excellent leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,AGREE WITH HIM!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. That's\Nnot gonna be my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons, hear me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I present to you our new\NDragon Lord... Ember!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well, Spike. With\NEmber as Dragon Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the ponies will be safe\Nand you've gained us
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a powerful ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And a new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, Ember said I could\Nwrite to her any time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I had questions\Nabout dragon culture!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,With this much information,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to write a\Nwhole book on dragons!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I gained tons of\Nideas for a new line
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of camouflage clothing! I\Nthink I'll call it camo-mod.
